Agent Result R6 Class

Source: R/agent-result.R
AgentResult.Rd

Contains the result of an agent task execution, including the final response, conversation history, cost information, and all events that occurred during execution.

Public fields

response

The final text response from the agent

turns

List of conversation turns

cost

Cost information (list with input, output, cached, total)

events

List of all AgentEvent objects from execution

duration

Execution duration in seconds

stop_reason

Reason the agent stopped
